That is...insane. The modern update features all the classics - Reed and Sue Richards, Johnny Storm and Ben Grimm - with new twists and exciting updates to many of the original tropes that made Marvel s famous and all with clear love and respect for Stan Lee and Jack Kirby's creations.

This is every issue of the series in digital copies by Empire scanners, along with 3 Annuals. The first 40 issues are HD/HR copies by AnHeroGold; there were also APG versions of these but I opted for the better quality editions for this pack. The remaining issues 41-60 are the 1280x rips by AnPymGold. Of the three annuals, two are by Cypher-Empire and the remaining is by APG. 
Massive thanks to all the Empire peeps for their work; please seed and enjoy!
